# SPR-TC-SHE-100023-gal-info-out-001

## Summary

**Test dataset:** [TD-SHE-000008-SHE-reconciliation](TD-SHE-000008-SHE-reconciliation.html)

**Test procedure:** The SHE Reconciliation pipeline was run on this tile (index 90346), using as input the shear measurements obtained from running the SHE Analysis pipeline on all overlapping observations. The resulting shear estimates table for LensMC was manually compared with the MER Final Catalog for this tile to check that all objects in the latter were present in the former.

**Test result:** **NOK**

## Detailed test results

The number of objects in each catalog was first compared, finding the following numbers:
  * Reconciled LensMC Measurements: 9179
  * MER Final Catalog: 9706

The differing numbers of objects here mean that at minimum 527 objects which are present in the MER Final Catalog are absent from the Reconciled LensMC Measurements catalog, so this test is deemed a failure.

Further investigation revealed that all objects present in the Reconciled LensMC Measurements catalog are also present in the MER Final Catalog. Conversely, 527 objects present in the latter are not present in the former. The full list of such objects' IDs is:
